Package model

Class Schedule

java.lang.Object
model.Schedule
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Schedule extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a doctor's schedule, including working time slots and appointments. Provides functionality for managing appointments and maintaining availability for up to 30 days in advance.
Since:
2024-11-18
Version:
1.0
Author:
Hoo Jing Huan, Tan Wen Rong
